# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WHITELIST dockerignore for Dockerfile.dev
#
# BuildKit picks `<Dockerfile>.dockerignore` over a root .dockerignore
# when both exist, so this file applies only to `Dockerfile.dev`
# builds. Prod builds use `Dockerfile.prod.dockerignore` separately.
#
# Dev only needs `docker-entrypoint.sh` from the build context;
# the rest of the source tree is bind-mounted into the container at
# runtime via `compose.dev.yaml` (`.:/app`).
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 1. Exclude everything by default
*

# 2. Re-include the only file Dockerfile.dev COPYs from context
!docker-entrypoint.sh
